name "subsec:Block-VII.-Foreign"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The foreign economy has so-called Armington demand of the domestic export
 good.
 We write the 
\series bold
block
\series default
 as:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Inputs: 
\series default
\emph on

\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ P_{t}^{F}\right\} ,$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \chi_{t}\right\} $
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ P_{t}^{X}\right\} $
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

